SUMMARY:Slunečný pofel @ Bqm
DESCRIPTION:<strong>Event details:</strong> https://cssz.ch/events/slunecny-pofel/\n<strong>Location:</strong> <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/bqDsM5dpDLDDRoGg8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">bQm Culture Café & Bar</a>\n<strong>Coordinator:</strong> Klára Kolářová (<a class="link" href="mailto:klara.kolarova@cssz.ch" target="_blank" rel="noopener">klara.kolarova@cssz.ch</a>)\n\nJoin us for Slunečný pofel at the bQm bar! ☀️ Whether you want to take a break from your studies or just catch up with the Czech and Slovak community in Zurich over a beer, this is the place to be 🍻. It’s a great chance to meet new faces and enjoy the relaxed atmosphere of bQm. We look forward to seeing you all there! 🎉
